data.enContent:
The table below lists APIs that can be used for logistics management.

API name Description
GetShipmentProviders Get the list of all active shipping providers, which is needed when working with the SetStatusToPackedByMarketplace call.
GetOrderTrace Query logistic detail for seller erp with seller id, order id and locale info. This api is only available in the state after ready to ship.
